AcyclicDigraphGenerator - Class in generator
Iterator to generate directed acyclic graphs (DAGs) for a given number of vertices reading from txt files such as the ones that can be found in the Acyclic graphs section at http://users.cecs.anu.edu.au/~bdm/data/digraphs.html.
